Akinwumi Adesina, president of the African Development Bank (AfDB), met with President Muhammadu Buhari at the presidential villa, Abuja, on Tuesday afternoon. Adesina, a former minister of agriculture, is the first Nigerian to occupy the top job at the development finance institution. He has served in several high-profile positions internationally, including that of the Rockefeller Foundation. He is currently serving a second term as AfDB president, which will elapse in 2025. Below are photos of the meeting: <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-691397" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-691401" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="400" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Buhari-and-Akinwunmi-Adesina-2-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes=